# The Bull API image builds from the REPO ROOT context so it can compile the
# bull-core parse sidecar (Rust/core). Keep the context lean — only BullAPI/ and
# Rust/core/ source are consumed; everything heavy or irrelevant is excluded.

.git
**/.DS_Store
**/node_modules

# iOS app, prebuilt native libs, local build output — unused by the API image
BullSwift
BullSwift.xcodeproj
BullWorkoutLiveActivityExtension
build
tmp
Scripts
docs

# Prebuilt device/sim static libs and the 13G+ Rust build cache
Rust/iphoneos
Rust/iphonesimulator
Rust/core/target

# Secrets / env — provided at runtime, never baked into the image
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# Docs
**/*.md

# BullAPI local-only
BullAPI/bundles
BullAPI/test
